For your Costa Rican fans it is a dream come true. Pearl Jam will play in Costa Rica. Do you realize what your fans are experiencing?
The journey to Costa Rica is also our dream, which becomes a reality.
In South and Central America we are barely the second time and the experience so far has been great.
I've only been to Costa Rica once, on vacation, and it's a beautiful country, and I believe we'll be able to stay here for a few days.
So we're so excited to be able to bring you our music.
I wonder, because here they literally love the group, the fans are experiencing these days of preparation very intensively.
What do you say to your biggest fans?
Thank you for having been with us for so many years.
It took us almost 21 years to get to Costa Rica. Thank you for waiting so long and we're sorry it took us so long.
Some people already call the concert the biggest show of the year.
Does it put more pressure on you?
