We are really looking forward to this concert.
We love this country, we love surfing, we like the jungle. For both activities, Costa Rica is the best country in the world.
How did you get to know Costa Rica and its surfing waves?
We have a lot of friends surfers and I have a good friend who lives in Tamarindo. The waves here are incredible.
My friends go surfing in Costa Rica or Nicaragua or Mexico. These are the best places to surf. So we learned about Costa Rica, through people who love surfing.
If we look at your tour, you've prepared a huge show with a lot of songs.
What were you planning for your presentation in Costa Rica?
Since we have never played here, we have no restrictions that we could not do.
We will try to perform the best show with a variety of tracks. We will try to play a few songs from each album and introduce our fans to a good and diverse repertoire.
You never repeat a repertoire.
- Why?
