Dactyloscopy is an exact science, without the possibility of a mistake, which can play a key role in deciding crimes.
In addition to identifying the dead, these people help investigate criminal acts such as theft or murder and confirm the identity of the arrested persons.
When caught, a lot of delinquents present false documents or have no papers at all.
